======================================
Ansible Introduction with Installation
======================================
RHEL SYSTEM ROLES TERMINOLOGY
    # Ansible Playbook
    # Inventory
    # Control Node
    # Manage Nodes

Control Nodes:
    1. Install Red Hat Ansible
        # yum install ansible*
        or
        # yum install ansible-core

    2. Verify ansible is installed on the system (check from control node)
        # ansible --version

    3. Verify the "ansible_python_version" on the localhost by using "setup" moudel. (from control node)
        # ansible -m setup localhost 
        or
        # ansible -m setup localhost | grep ansible_python_version
    
Manage Hosts Side:
    1. Enable and install pythone
        # yum install python*

_____________ThankYou_______________
